あの、にこたんもね、3Dになったということで。
Since Nico-tan got her 3D model as well.

174
00:20:22,328 --> 00:20:24,028
なりました！はい！
I did! Yes!

175
00:20:24,028 --> 00:20:29,228
で、にこたんが「いつかルイ先輩の隣で歌いたい」って言ってくれてたので、
And since Nico-tan said she wanted to sing next to her Lui-senpai someday,

176
00:20:29,228 --> 00:20:32,228
ありがとうございまーす！
Thank you so much!

177
00:20:32,228 --> 00:20:35,228
なので、今日は、お呼びさせていただきました！
I decided to invite her here today!

178
00:20:35,228 --> 00:20:37,428
ありがとうございます、本当に！
Thank you so much, really!

179
00:20:37,428 --> 00:20:42,428
いや、めちゃくちゃカッコいい曲を歌っていただきましたが、皆さんいかがでしたか？
We got to perform such a cool song together. What did everyone think?

180
00:20:42,428 --> 00:20:44,528
いや、本当、嬉しかったです。にこたん良かったねって。
I was honestly so happy. They're saying, "Good for you, Nico-tan."

181
00:20:44,528 --> 00:20:47,328
いやいや、もうにこたんのことはいいんです！
No, no, never mind about Nico-tan!

182
00:20:47,328 --> 00:20:48,428
にこたん良かったねって。
"Good for you, Nico-tan."

183
00:20:48,428 --> 00:20:51,528
そんなことよりですね、ルイ先輩、にこたんなんかより！
More importantly, Lui-senpai, forget about Nico-tan!

184
00:20:51,528 --> 00:20:55,528
今日重大告知もあるし、新衣装もあるんですよ！
There's a major announcement today, and a new outfit!

185
00:20:55,528 --> 00:20:57,228
そうなんです。新衣装もあるんです。
That's right. There's a new outfit too.

186
00:20:57,228 --> 00:20:58,428
出るんでしたっけ？
Is it coming out?

187
00:20:58,428 --> 00:21:02,428
これね、たくさんね、ここのハッシュタグ、
Yes. Please use this hashtag:

188
00:21:02,428 --> 00:21:04,228
「#鷹嶺ルイ超重大生誕LIVE」ってありますんで、
"#TakaneLuiSuperMajorBirthdayLIVE"

189
00:21:04,228 --> 00:21:08,428
それでたくさんたくさん、もうポストしてくれたら嬉しいなと思うんですけど、
I'd be so happy if you'd post a lot using it.

190
00:21:08,428 --> 00:21:09,728
今日はたくさん、告知もありますし。
We have so many announcements today.

191
00:21:09,728 --> 00:21:11,728
そうですよね！
That's right!

192
00:21:11,728 --> 00:21:15,728
いや、にこたん気になるのも、もちろん重大告知の、デカさも気になるんですけど、
I mean, I'm curious about Nico-tan and how big the major announcement is, but...

193
00:21:15,728 --> 00:21:18,428
新衣装がやっぱりね、気になる。
...I'm really curious about the new outfit.

194
00:21:18,428 --> 00:21:21,328
やっぱりルイ先輩といえば、こう、ちょっとダークネスな感じなのかなとか。
When you think of Lui-senpai, you think of a sort of dark style, right?

195
00:21:21,328 --> 00:21:24,728
黒い、黒系なのかな、みたいな。ああ、なるほど、なるほど。
Like black or dark colors. Ah, I see, I see.

196
00:21:24,728 --> 00:21:27,228
そう思いますよね？
Don't you all agree?

197
00:21:27,228 --> 00:21:28,728
はい。
Yes.

198
00:21:28,728 --> 00:21:30,228
ま、それもあります。
Well, there is that aspect.

199
00:21:30,228 --> 00:21:31,728
おお！それも？
Oh! That too?

200
00:21:31,728 --> 00:21:35,228
ということは？最初ね、あの、固定でも書かせていただいたんですけど、
Which means...? I mentioned this in the pinned comment, but...

201
00:21:35,228 --> 00:21:39,228
あの、新衣装は、最初はサブカラー。
...the new outfit starts with the sub-colors.

202
00:21:39,228 --> 00:21:43,228
ええ？！で、ちょっと清楚な感じの衣装になっております。
What?! It has a somewhat elegant and pure feel to it.

203
00:21:43,228 --> 00:21:46,228
え？それもあるって、他、他にもあるってこと？はい。
Huh? You have that, but does that mean there are others too? Yes.

204
00:21:46,228 --> 00:21:49,228
めちゃくちゃ大量にサブを用意しておりますので、最後までね、楽しんで...
I've prepared a huge variety of options, so look forward to it...

205
00:21:49,228 --> 00:21:51,528
キャー！なんか、なんかすごい騒いでる。
*screams* Wow, you're getting super excited.

206
00:21:51,528 --> 00:21:53,428
おかしい、サブ、サブも？うん。
This is crazy! Sub... sub-colors too?! Yep.

207
00:21:53,428 --> 00:21:56,428
もういいや、今日は来てくれてありがとう。
Anyway, thank you so much for coming today.

208
00:21:56,428 --> 00:21:59,428
あ、分かりました！にこたん楽屋で応援してます！それでは！
Ah, alright! Nico-tan will cheer you on from the dressing room! Goodbye!

209
00:21:59,428 --> 00:22:01,428
あ、違います、違います。そ、そちらの舞踏会会場なんで、
Ah, wait, not that way. That way leads to the ballroom, so...

210
00:22:01,428 --> 00:22:04,228
ここ、ダメなんですか？にこたん。はい。
Is Nico-tan not allowed in here? Yes.

211
00:22:04,228 --> 00:22:07,428
にこたんは呼んでない。招待状、もらってないでしょ？
Nico-tan wasn't invited. You didn't get an invitation, right?

212
00:22:07,428 --> 00:22:09,328
もらってないけど...うん。
Well, no, but... Exactly.

213
00:22:09,328 --> 00:22:12,428
じゃあ、あの、すいませんが楽屋の方にあちらから。嫌だー！
So, excuse me, but please head to the dressing room from over there. No way!

214
00:22:12,428 --> 00:22:15,428
はい、スタッフさん、お願いします！はい！
Staff, please assist her! Yes!

215
00:22:15,428 --> 00:22:19,228
ルイ先輩、タッチ、タッチだけでも！ありがとう、ありがとう。
Lui-senpai, just a high-five! Just a high-five! Thank you, thank you.

216
00:22:19,228 --> 00:22:22,228
頑張ってください！ありがとうね、ありがとうね。
Do your best! Thank you so much.

217
00:22:22,228 --> 00:22:25,228
ありがとうね。
Thank you.

218
00:22:25,228 --> 00:22:31,228
ということで、にこたんに来ていただきました。はい、新衣装もね、たくさん見せていきますので、
And so, Nico-tan paid us a visit. Yes, I'll be showing off lots of new outfits,

219
00:22:31,228 --> 00:22:34,228
最後まで楽しんでいただけたらなと思います。楽屋のにこたんも楽しんでくださいね！
so I hope you enjoy the show until the very end. Nico-tan in the dressing room, enjoy yourself too!

220
00:22:34,228 --> 00:22:38,228
それでは聞いてください、ZIG-ZAG。
Now then, please listen to "ZIG-ZAG".

221
00:22:52,228 --> 00:22:54,228
One, two, three, four

222
00:23:02,228 --> 00:23:06,328
狂わせて 囁いた
You whispered to drive me mad,

223
00:23:06,328 --> 00:23:10,328
こびりついて離れぬは
Clinging to me and never leaving,

224
00:23:10,328 --> 00:23:14,728
無味無臭の生活が 思いだせないや
I can't even remember my tasteless, odorless life.

225
00:23:14,728 --> 00:23:18,728
忘れたいから歌った
I sang because I wanted to forget...

226
00:23:18,728 --> 00:23:23,228
恨むことも 憎むことも
Resenting or even hating someone...

227
00:23:23,228 --> 00:23:27,728
賢く割に合わなかった
...was too clever and didn't pay off.

228
00:23:27,728 --> 00:23:31,728
これが君の結末ならば
If this is your end,

229
00:23:31,728 --> 00:23:35,728
笑ってしまいたい
I just want to laugh it off.

230
00:23:35,728 --> 00:23:38,228
嘘、嘘、嘘
Lies, lies, lies.

231
00:23:38,228 --> 00:23:39,728
嘘つき
Liar.

232
00:23:39,728 --> 00:23:43,228
痛い、痛い、痛いな 奇跡とかちょっとのぞいちゃって
It hurts, it hurts, having caught a glimpse of a miracle...

233
00:23:43,228 --> 00:23:47,228
もう嫌、嫌、嫌 立ちが悪いわね
...I'm sick, sick, sick of it. You have a nasty streak, don't you?

234
00:23:47,228 --> 00:23:52,228
無い、無い、無いな おかしいとこ全部えぐりとって
There's none, none, none. Gouging out all the strange parts...

235
00:23:52,228 --> 00:23:56,228
悪評だって結構 好きに呼んでいいよ
...bad reputation is fine, call me whatever you like.

236
00:23:56,228 --> 00:24:00,728
トラウマにバイバイしたいの Death, death, death
I want to say bye-bye to my trauma. Death, death, death.

237
00:24:08,728 --> 00:24:13,228
私 甘え上手になれなかった
I couldn't become good at playing coddled,

238
00:24:13,228 --> 00:24:17,728
可愛げとかが足りなかった 後悔か？うるさいよもういい
I lacked cuteness. "Regrets?" Shut up, enough already.

239
00:24:17,728 --> 00:24:22,228
過去は過去だと割り切っちゃえば きっと良いことあるさとか
If I just write off the past, "surely good things will happen" and so on...

240
00:24:22,228 --> 00:24:26,228
これくらい百も承知だ
I know all of this all too well!

241
00:24:26,228 --> 00:24:30,228
願うことも 祈ることも
Wishing or even praying...

242
00:24:30,228 --> 00:24:34,228
許されないから黒く染めた
...aren't allowed, so I dyed it black.

243
00:24:34,228 --> 00:24:38,428
元の色も思い出せない
I can't even remember the original color.

244
00:24:38,428 --> 00:24:42,228
狂った運命の
This twisted fate's...

245
00:24:42,228 --> 00:24:45,728
糸、糸、意図、糸
...thread, thread, thread, thread.

246
00:24:45,728 --> 00:24:49,228
痛い、痛い、痛いな 悲劇のヒロイン気取っちゃって
It hurts, it hurts, pretending to be the tragic heroine...

247
00:24:49,228 --> 00:24:53,228
もう嫌、嫌、嫌 諦めちゃえばいいのに
...I'm sick, sick, sick of it. Even though I should just give up.

248
00:24:53,228 --> 00:24:57,228
会いたい、会いたい、会いたいな 信号が赤になっちゃって
I want to meet, meet, meet you. The traffic light turned red...

249
00:24:57,228 --> 00:25:01,228
明日またきっと
...and surely, tomorrow again...

250
00:25:01,045 --> 00:25:02,845
壊すけどいいの？
I'm going to break it, is that okay?

251
00:25:02,845 --> 00:25:05,545
囚われ舞い散るの
Trapped and fluttering away.

252
00:25:05,545 --> 00:25:08,045
デス デス デ デ デ デス
Death, death, de-de-de-death!

253
00:25:33,145 --> 00:25:39,245
夢の中で君と手を繋いでいるの
In my dreams, I am holding hands with you,

254
00:25:39,245 --> 00:25:45,845
何も知らないあの頃の二人のままで
just like the two of us back then, knowing nothing.

255
00:25:45,845 --> 00:25:52,145
でも分かっているよ すぐに覚めてしまうと
But I know it well, that I will wake up soon.

256
00:25:52,145 --> 00:25:56,045
それならばいっそ 君の手でそっと
If that's the case, then rather, by your hand, softly...

257
00:25:56,045 --> 00:25:58,545
トドメを刺して
deal the finishing blow.

258
00:25:58,545 --> 00:26:02,045
ほら 今 今 今
Look, now, now, now!

259
00:26:02,045 --> 00:26:06,545
奪いたい奪いたい奪いたいな 奇跡とかちょっと望んじゃって
I want to steal, steal, steal it, hoping for a bit of a miracle,

260
00:26:06,545 --> 00:26:08,845
もう 嫌 嫌 嫌 嫌 嫌
No more, no, no, no, no, no!

261
00:26:08,845 --> 00:26:11,545
タチが悪いわ
This is so nasty.

262
00:26:11,545 --> 00:26:16,045
足りない足りない足りないな おかしいとこ全部抉り取って
It's not enough, not enough, gouge out all the strange parts,

263
00:26:16,045 --> 00:26:18,045
拍手喝采で結構
applause is perfectly fine.

264
00:26:18,045 --> 00:26:20,045
お好きに呼んでいいよ
Call me whatever you like.

265
00:26:20,045 --> 00:26:22,045
囚われる前に バイバイしたいの
Before I get caught, I want to say bye-bye.

266
00:26:22,045 --> 00:26:24,545
デス デス デ デ デ デス
Death, death, de-de-de-death,

267
00:26:24,545 --> 00:26:27,045
デス デス デ デ デ デス
death, death, de-de-de-death!

268
00:27:10,045 --> 00:27:16,045
アイのシナリオ
[Song: Ai no Scenario]

269
00:27:20,045 --> 00:27:23,045
世界欺く揺るぎない正義
An unwavering justice that deceives the world,

270
00:27:23,045 --> 00:27:29,045
ほどいて真実この手の中
unravels, bringing the truth into these hands.

271
00:27:29,045 --> 00:27:30,045
大胆不敵な影が華麗に踊る
A daring, fearless shadow dances gracefully,

272
00:27:30,045 --> 00:27:40,545
君が隠してる秘密いつか聞かせてよ
tell me the secret you're hiding someday.

273
00:27:40,545 --> 00:27:46,045
伸ばした手で触れる事は誰もできない
No one can reach out and touch it,

274
00:27:46,045 --> 00:27:51,545
君が隠してる世界僕に見せてよ
show me the world you're hiding.

275
00:27:51,545 --> 00:27:54,045
揺れる難解な心
A wavering, complex heart,

276
00:27:54,045 --> 00:27:58,545
解き明かして奪うその瞳
solving the mystery, stealing away those eyes.

277
00:27:58,545 --> 00:28:01,545
不安がって泣いてたって見つかんないよ
Even if you cry in anxiety, you won't find it,

278
00:28:01,545 --> 00:28:06,545
狙う真実はどこへ消えた
where did the truth we're aiming for vanish to?

279
00:28:06,545 --> 00:28:08,545
たとえ
Even if...

280
00:28:08,545 --> 00:28:13,045
世界欺く解答（こたえ）だとしても
even if it's an answer that deceives the world,

281
00:28:13,045 --> 00:28:17,845
信じて差し出す掌
I'll believe and hold out my palm.

282
00:28:17,845 --> 00:28:22,045
決して逃げない怖くは無いから
I'll never run away, because I'm not afraid,

283
00:28:22,045 --> 00:28:27,045
目を開け弱さをかき消すんだ
open your eyes and drown out the weakness!

284
00:28:36,545 --> 00:28:41,545
繰り返される運命に君は気づいてる？
Have you noticed the repeating fate?

285
00:28:41,545 --> 00:28:47,545
僕が隠してる秘密いつか聞かせるよ
I'll tell you the secret I'm hiding someday.

286
00:28:47,545 --> 00:28:53,045
歩み寄る偽りの影君は知らない
You don't know the false shadow approaching,

287
00:28:53,045 --> 00:28:58,045
芽生えた記憶は絡む必然の棘で
the budding memories are tangled in inevitable thorns.

288
00:28:58,045 --> 00:29:00,845
守りたい想いでただ
Simply with the desire to protect,

289
00:29:00,845 --> 00:29:05,045
立ち向かって解（ほど）くその絆
I'll stand tall and untie those bonds.

290
00:29:05,045 --> 00:29:09,545
何度だって助けるって揺るぎはしないよ
I will save you as many times as it takes, I won't waver,

291
00:29:09,545 --> 00:29:14,045
隠す真実はどこへ消えた
where did the hidden truth vanish to?

292
00:29:14,045 --> 00:29:16,045
たとえ
Even if...

293
00:29:16,045 --> 00:29:20,045
世界を敵に回したとしても
even if I turn the whole world against me,

294
00:29:20,045 --> 00:29:24,545
「信じて」僕だけ未来も
believe in only me, and our future too,

295
00:29:24,545 --> 00:29:29,245
決して逃げない迷いは無いから
I'll never run away, because I have no doubts,

296
00:29:29,245 --> 00:29:35,545
シナリオ壊して抗うんだ
I'll destroy the scenario and fight back!

297
00:30:13,665 --> 00:30:18,665
世界を敵に回したとしても
Even if I make the world my enemy,

298
00:30:18,965 --> 00:30:24,165
信じて 差し出す 手のひら
trust me, and hold out your hand.

299
00:30:24,365 --> 00:30:29,665
決して離さない 想いは届いた
I will never let go, my feelings have reached you.

300
00:30:29,965 --> 00:30:35,165
結んだ運命 この手の中
This bound destiny is in our hands.

301
00:30:35,365 --> 00:30:40,165
繰り返された 答えだとしても
Even if it's an answer that repeats itself...

302
00:30:45,665 --> 00:30:47,365
決して
Never...

303
00:30:47,365 --> 00:30:52,165
逃げない 怖くは無いから
will I run away, because there's nothing to fear.

304
00:30:54,665 --> 00:30:56,965
抗うんだ
I will fight back.

305
00:31:21,665 --> 00:31:26,665
何度も 何度も 走り続けるよ
Over and over again, I'll keep running on!

306
00:31:27,965 --> 00:31:29,465
Wake up! 闘志オンにして
Wake up! Turn on your fighting spirit!

307
00:31:29,465 --> 00:31:30,965
Shift up! ギア回して
Shift up! Shift the gears!

308
00:31:30,965 --> 00:31:32,465
Speed up! 羽ばたいて
Speed up! Spread your wings!

309
00:31:32,465 --> 00:31:34,165
U.M.A. NEW WORLD!

310
00:31:34,165 --> 00:31:35,565
Jump up! てっぺんへ
Jump up! To the very top!

311
00:31:35,665 --> 00:31:36,965
Turn up! 声合わせて
Turn up! Join our voices!

312
00:31:37,065 --> 00:31:38,465
Dream on! 未来繋いで
Dream on! Connect our futures!

313
00:31:38,565 --> 00:31:40,165
U.M.A. NEW WORLD!

314
00:31:40,365 --> 00:31:43,165
最高潮コンディション 闘志ガンガン尖ってこう
Peak condition! Let's sharpen our fighting spirit!

315
00:31:43,165 --> 00:31:46,165
栄光のチャンピオン 虎視眈々と狙ってこう
Glory's champion! Let's watch vigilantly for our chance!

316
00:31:46,365 --> 00:31:47,865
ハイペースにマイペース
High pace, my pace,

317
00:31:47,965 --> 00:31:49,465
気合いレースに超集中
super focused on this energetic race!

318
00:31:49,465 --> 00:31:51,465
駆ける背中は限界突破 ハートに火をつけて
Running past limits, setting our hearts on fire!

319
00:31:51,465 --> 00:31:53,165
U.M.A. Let's go!

320
00:31:53,165 --> 00:31:56,165
最高潮アディクション 互い掲げた勝負
Climax addiction! The challenge we laid down together,

321
00:31:56,165 --> 00:31:59,165
千載一遇のチャンスを 全力出して掴んでこう
let's give it our all and seize this once-in-a-lifetime chance!

322
00:31:59,165 --> 00:32:00,565
ハイペースにマイペース
High pace, my pace,

323
00:32:00,565 --> 00:32:02,165
気合いレースに猛集中
intensely focused on this energetic race!

324
00:32:02,165 --> 00:32:05,665
駆けるフォームをセットして 熱くちぎってこう
Set your running form and tear through passionately!

325
00:32:07,165 --> 00:32:10,165
友と二人 競い合った 風の中でも
Competing together with a friend, even through the wind,

326
00:32:10,165 --> 00:32:13,165
大きな背中 追いかけてた 雨の中でも
chasing that great back, even in the rain,

327
00:32:13,165 --> 00:32:15,965
何百何千回と 積み重ねてきた
hundreds, thousands of times, we have built this up.

328
00:32:16,165 --> 00:32:19,365
だからどこまでも遠く どこまでも高く
So, no matter how far, no matter how high,

329
00:32:19,365 --> 00:32:23,165
誰よりも早く 誰よりも強く
faster than anyone, stronger than anyone!

330
00:32:23,165 --> 00:32:25,665
さあ、今！
Now, let's go!

331
00:32:25,665 --> 00:32:28,665
駆け出した想いは もう止まらない
The feelings we started running with won't stop!

332
